This Chrome extension, Bitwise Account Manager (BAM), does not collect
or leak user information. It uses no third-party services and loads no
external resources.

User-supplied data including trading API credentials are encrypted
with a user-supplied password and stored locally.

BAM exposes no interfaces for a host application to extract or tamper
with sensitive API secrets.

BAM sends signed API requests directly to crypto-exchanges from the
Chrome browser without relying on any relay server.
